- //access to wikiPageCtrl functions or data
h1 {{ properties.pagename }}
div(class="row")
  div(class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3")
    div(class="col-xs-12")
      div(class="separate-vert-medium")
        div(class="panel panel-default")
          div(class="panel-heading text-large") ISSUE
          div(class="panel-body")
            div Short Description of the issue
      div(class="separate-vert-medium")
        div(class="panel panel-default")
          div(class="panel-heading text-large") ENVIRONMENT
          div(class="panel-body")
            div Information in regards to the environment this issue happens on, or version-specific information
      div(class="separate-vert-medium")
        div(class="panel panel-default")
          div(class="panel-heading text-large") RESOLUTION
          div(class="panel-body")
            div How is this resolved?
      div(class="separate-vert-medium")
        div(class="panel panel-default")
          div(class="panel-heading text-large") CAUSE
          div(class="panel-body")
            div Explain why this issue occurs.
      div(class="separate-vert-medium")
        div(class="panel panel-default")
          div(class="panel-heading text-large") TROUBLESHOOTING
          div(class="panel-body")
            div How can you troubleshoot this issue?